  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study efficacy and safety of deep brain stimulation of the cingulate cortex in 20
      patients with treatment resistant major depression will be investigated. In addition, the
      stress axis, the cortical GABAergic system, neurotrophins and event-related potentials will
      be assessed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
